dcterms:description: A collection of climate records of North America containing monthly observations of 17 variables such as carbon dioxide and temperature spanning from 1990 to 2001 across 125 observation locations, resulting in a 138 × 17 × 125 tensor.
dcterms:title: Comprehensive Climate Data Set (CCDS)

dcterms:description: Collected from the meteorological office in the UK, this dataset contains monthly measurements of 5 variables in 16 stations across the UK from 1960 to 2000, resulting in a 492 × 5 × 16 tensor; measures were scaled to have zero mean and unitary variance.
dcterms:title: Meteo-UK Data Set

dcterms:description: Synthetic data generated for experiments, consisting of a 30 × 30 × 30 tensor with Tucker-rank equal to (6, 6, 6) and a 4-th order tensor of size 12 × 12 × 12 × 12 with TT-rank equal to (1, 6, 6, 6, 1).
dcterms:title: Synthetic Data
